article_id:1182,category_name:News,title_name:Original Wallpaper Now Available!,image_path:,message:<div>We added new original wallpaper to the Wallpapers section under the Special header on the Dragalia Lost official website at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585288800"></span>!</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/c5804640cf4fcc548b631efbd28edaa7.jpg"></div><div><br></div><div>▼You can download the original wallpaper here:</div><div><a href="https://dragalialost.com/en-gb/special/wallpaper/">https://dragalialost.com/en-gb/special/wallpaper/</a></div><div><br></div><div>・The only available size for the new original wallpaper is 1920&times;1080.</div><div>・These images are for your personal use. Please remember to follow our Code of Conduct: <a href="https://www.nintendo.com/nintendoaccount/code-of-conduct/">https://www.nintendo.com/nintendoaccount/code-of-conduct/</a></div><div>・The method for setting the image as your wallpaper may differ between browsers and OS versions. For information on how to set the image as your wallpaper, please refer to the help information for your computer.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1585288800,update_time1585271418